@startuml SD_07_SepayPayment
' ============================================================
' SEQUENCE DIAGRAM - Thanh toán SePay VietQR + Webhook
' FR-20, FR-21, FR-22: QR Payment → Webhook → Ticket Generation
' ============================================================

title **SD-07: Thanh toán VietQR qua SePay\n(Payment + Webhook + Ticket Generation)**

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam maxmessagesize 180
skinparam sequence {
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #E8EAF6
    ParticipantBorderColor #283593
    ArrowColor #283593
}

actor "Attendee" as User #LightBlue
participant "Browser\n(JSP)" as Browser #LightYellow
participant "PaymentServlet\n(Controller)" as PayCtrl #E8EAF6
participant "PaymentFactory" as Factory #FFF3E0
participant "SepayPaymentService\n(Strategy)" as SepaySvc #E8F5E9
participant "OrderService" as OrderSvc #E8F5E9
participant "TicketService" as TicketSvc #E0F7FA
participant "WebhookServlet\n(Callback)" as Webhook #FCE4EC
box "External" #F5F5F5
    participant "SePay API\n(Payment Gateway)" as SePay #FFCDD2
    participant "Ngân hàng\n(User's Bank)" as Bank #FFCDD2
end box
database "SQL Server" as DB #F3E5F5

== Phase 1: Tạo QR Code Thanh toán ==

User -> Browser: Truy cập trang thanh toán
Browser -> PayCtrl: GET /checkout/payment\n?orderId={orderId}
activate PayCtrl

PayCtrl -> OrderSvc: getOrder(orderId)
activate OrderSvc
OrderSvc -> DB: SELECT * FROM Orders\nWHERE orderId = ?\nAND customerId = ?\nAND status = 'pending'
activate DB
DB --> OrderSvc: Order
deactivate DB
OrderSvc --> PayCtrl: Order
deactivate OrderSvc

PayCtrl -> Factory: getProvider("sepay")
activate Factory
Factory --> PayCtrl: SepayPaymentService
deactivate Factory

PayCtrl -> SepaySvc: createPayment(order)
activate SepaySvc
SepaySvc -> SepaySvc: Build transfer info:\nbank = "MBBank"\naccount = "0389966997"\namount = order.totalAmount\ncontent = "ST" + order.orderCode\n(unique payment reference)

SepaySvc -> SepaySvc: Generate VietQR URL:\nhttps://img.vietqr.io/image/\n{bankId}-{account}-compact2.png\n?amount={amount}\n&addInfo={content}\n&accountName={name}

SepaySvc --> PayCtrl: PaymentResult\n{qrUrl, bankInfo, amount,\ncontent, expiresAt=now+15min}
deactivate SepaySvc

PayCtrl -> DB: UPDATE Orders SET\npaymentMethod = 'sepay_qr',\npaymentExpiry = NOW() + 15min
PayCtrl --> Browser: Forward → payment.jsp\n(QR image, bank info, countdown timer)
deactivate PayCtrl
Browser --> User: Hiển thị:\n- QR Code VietQR\n- Thông tin CK (STK, ngân hàng)\n- Nội dung CK: ST{orderCode}\n- Đếm ngược 15 phút

== Phase 2: Khách thanh toán qua ngân hàng ==

User -> Browser: Mở app Banking\nquét QR code
Browser -> Bank: Quét QR → Điền thông tin CK
activate Bank
User -> Bank: Xác nhận chuyển khoản
Bank -> Bank: Xử lý giao dịch
Bank --> User: ✅ Chuyển khoản thành công
Bank -> SePay: Notification giao dịch mới
deactivate Bank

== Phase 3: SePay Webhook Callback ==

SePay -> Webhook: POST /api/sepay/webhook\nHeaders:\n  Authorization: Apikey {API_KEY}\nBody: {\n  "id": 12345,\n  "transferType": "in",\n  "transferAmount": 500000,\n  "content": "ST ORD-ABC123",\n  "referenceCode": "FT24xxx"\n}
activate Webhook

' --- Security Validation ---
Webhook -> Webhook: **Security Checks:**\n1. Validate API Key header\n2. Check Content-Type\n3. Validate body size < 10KB\n4. Check IP whitelist (optional)

alt #FFE0E0 Invalid API Key
    Webhook --> SePay: HTTP 401 Unauthorized
else #E8F5E9 Valid Request

    ' --- Extract Order Code ---
    Webhook -> Webhook: Parse "content" field:\nExtract orderCode from\n"ST ORD-ABC123"\n→ orderCode = "ORD-ABC123"

    ' --- Find Order ---
    Webhook -> OrderSvc: findByOrderCode(orderCode)
    activate OrderSvc
    OrderSvc -> DB: SELECT * FROM Orders\nWHERE orderCode = ?
    activate DB
    DB --> OrderSvc: Order
    deactivate DB
    OrderSvc --> Webhook: Order
    deactivate OrderSvc

    alt #FFE0E0 Order Not Found
        Webhook --> SePay: HTTP 200 OK\n(acknowledge, no action)
    else #E8F5E9 Order Found

        ' --- Validate Amount ---
        Webhook -> Webhook: Validate:\ntransferAmount == order.totalAmount?\n(tolerance check)

        alt #FFE0E0 Amount Mismatch
            Webhook -> DB: INSERT INTO PaymentLogs\n(status='AMOUNT_MISMATCH')
            Webhook --> SePay: HTTP 200 OK\n(log discrepancy)
        else #E8F5E9 Amount Matches

            ' --- Idempotency Check ---
            Webhook -> Webhook: Check order.status\n!= 'confirmed'\n(prevent double processing)

            alt order.status == 'confirmed'
                Webhook --> SePay: HTTP 200 OK\n(already processed)
            else order.status == 'pending'

                == Phase 4: Confirm Order + Generate Tickets ==

                Webhook -> OrderSvc: confirmOrder(orderId,\npaymentRef, transactionId)
                activate OrderSvc

                OrderSvc -> DB: **BEGIN TRANSACTION**
                activate DB

                OrderSvc -> DB: UPDATE Orders SET\nstatus = 'confirmed',\npaymentDate = GETDATE(),\npaymentRef = ?,\ntransactionId = ?

                ' --- Generate Individual Tickets ---
                OrderSvc -> TicketSvc: generateTickets(order)
                activate TicketSvc

                loop for each OrderItem (N tickets)
                    TicketSvc -> TicketSvc: Generate unique ticketCode:\n"TKT-" + UUID.randomUUID()\n.substring(0, 8).toUpperCase()

                    TicketSvc -> TicketSvc: Create QR payload:\nJWT.create()\n.withClaim("ticketCode", code)\n.withClaim("eventId", eventId)\n.sign(HMAC256(secret))

                    TicketSvc -> DB: INSERT INTO Tickets\n(ticketId, orderId, orderItemId,\nticketTypeId, ticketCode,\nqrCodeData, isCheckedIn=false,\ncreatedAt)
                end

                TicketSvc --> OrderSvc: List<Ticket> generated
                deactivate TicketSvc

                OrderSvc -> DB: COMMIT
                deactivate DB

                ' --- Send Notification ---
                OrderSvc -> DB: INSERT INTO Notifications\n(userId=customerId,\ntype='ORDER_CONFIRMED',\nmessage='Đơn hàng đã thanh toán\nthành công. Xem vé của bạn.')

                OrderSvc --> Webhook: Success
                deactivate OrderSvc

                Webhook -> DB: INSERT INTO PaymentLogs\n(orderId, status='SUCCESS',\ntransactionId, amount)

                Webhook --> SePay: HTTP 200 OK\n{"success": true}

            end
        end
    end
end

deactivate Webhook

== Phase 5: Attendee Kiểm tra kết quả ==

User -> Browser: Refresh trang thanh toán
Browser -> PayCtrl: GET /checkout/payment\n?orderId={orderId}
activate PayCtrl
PayCtrl -> OrderSvc: getOrder(orderId)
activate OrderSvc
OrderSvc -> DB: SELECT * FROM Orders
activate DB
DB --> OrderSvc: Order (status=confirmed)
deactivate DB
OrderSvc --> PayCtrl: Order
deactivate OrderSvc
PayCtrl --> Browser: Redirect → /tickets\n(Order confirmed!)
deactivate PayCtrl
Browser --> User: ✅ Thanh toán thành công!\nXem vé QR Code

@enduml
